This folder contains the support code for the NUCLEO-H743ZI board
(MB1137).


STM32CubeH7 Firmware Package
============================
This directory contians parts of STM32CubeH7 1.2.0, which are
relevant to the NUCLEO-H743ZI board. To preserve compatibilty
with STM32CubeH7, this directory preserves the sub-directory
structure of STM32CubeH7, so the relative paths should work for
the full version of STM32CubeH7 as well.
